+                "RGB" Exec /usr/X11R6/bin/xterm -e /bin/sh -c
'/usr/X11R6/bin/showrgb | /bin/awk "{ printf(\"#%02X%02X%02X\t\", \$$$$1,
\$$$$2, \$$$$3); for (i = 4; i <= NF; i++) printf \" \" \$i; print
\"\" }" | /usr/bin/less'

It's a bit messy but at least I don't have to keep track of external
scripts! 8-)

Have a nice day,

Neil

